    <div class="col-xs-12 debate-date">
        <strong>09 November 1954</strong>
    </div>

    <div class="col-xs-12 debate-date">Volume 532</div>

    <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12">
        <div class="container">
            <div id="debateContent">
                <div class="highlightedSearchTerms"></div>
                <div class="content-container">


<div class="content-item other-content">
        <!-- START statement -->
        <div class="statement col-md-9 hs_ColumnNumber content-container " >
                <span data-toggle="tooltip" data-hop-debug-tooltip class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign hidden hidden-xs" data-placement="bottom" title=" hs_ColumnNumber "></span>

<p class="hs_ColumnNumber"><span id="1039" class="column-number column-only" data-column-number="1039"></span></p>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            </div>
        <div class="clearfix"></div>
        <!-- END statement -->
</div>

<div class="content-item other-content">
        <!-- START statement -->
        <div class="statement col-md-9  content-container " id='contribution-c4f08abd-59f6-4600-9a6a-ef55338baff1'>
            
<p class="">45.</p>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            </div>
        <div class="clearfix"></div>
        <!-- END statement -->
</div><div class="content-item" id="contribution-d1fbdd40-e2f5-4b01-bb4c-4501a55243b9">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-d1fbdd40-e2f5-4b01-bb4c-4501a55243b9">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-d1fbdd40-e2f5-4b01-bb4c-4501a55243b9">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-d1fbdd40-e2f5-4b01-bb4c-4501a55243b9">
                Mr. Wyatt
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-d1fbdd40-e2f5-4b01-bb4c-4501a55243b9" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1954-11-09/debates/7c94ea06-d5eb-425c-864e-c148817f910d/NuclearAndAtomicExplosions#contribution-d1fbdd40-e2f5-4b01-bb4c-4501a55243b9">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">asked the Prime Minister after how many explosions, atomic and nuclear, and over what period, he is advised that a lethal atmosphere will be produced over substantial areas of the world.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-d1fbdd40-e2f5-4b01-bb4c-4501a55243b9" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1954-11-09/debates/7c94ea06-d5eb-425c-864e-c148817f910d/NuclearAndAtomicExplosions#contribution-d1fbdd40-e2f5-4b01-bb4c-4501a55243b9">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-a539ea02-8727-418d-92ee-03330ea38151">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-a539ea02-8727-418d-92ee-03330ea38151">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-a539ea02-8727-418d-92ee-03330ea38151">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-a539ea02-8727-418d-92ee-03330ea38151">
                The Prime Minister (Sir Winston Churchill)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-a539ea02-8727-418d-92ee-03330ea38151" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1954-11-09/debates/7c94ea06-d5eb-425c-864e-c148817f910d/NuclearAndAtomicExplosions#contribution-a539ea02-8727-418d-92ee-03330ea38151">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">An answer to this Question would depend on an accurate assessment of a variety of immeasurables. I am advised that from our present knowledge the number of major experimental explosions required to produce lethal risks over an area beyond that immediately affected by the explosion would be very large indeed. On the most cautious assumptions it would be, so I am advised, considerably greater than the number which could conceivably be employed in any tests likely to be made by the Powers who possess these weapons. Investigation into this problem is proceeding actively and continuously.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-a539ea02-8727-418d-92ee-03330ea38151" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1954-11-09/debates/7c94ea06-d5eb-425c-864e-c148817f910d/NuclearAndAtomicExplosions#contribution-a539ea02-8727-418d-92ee-03330ea38151">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-d8a99d3a-10bf-4a09-9fc5-55b9c4e216c9">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-d8a99d3a-10bf-4a09-9fc5-55b9c4e216c9">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-d8a99d3a-10bf-4a09-9fc5-55b9c4e216c9">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-d8a99d3a-10bf-4a09-9fc5-55b9c4e216c9">
                Mr. Wyatt
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-d8a99d3a-10bf-4a09-9fc5-55b9c4e216c9" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1954-11-09/debates/7c94ea06-d5eb-425c-864e-c148817f910d/NuclearAndAtomicExplosions#contribution-d8a99d3a-10bf-4a09-9fc5-55b9c4e216c9">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">I hope that the Prime Minister will not try to make jokes about this matter. [HON. MEMBERS: "Oh."] Is it not a fact that Dr. Adrian, at the British Association in September, said: <blockquote><q>"â€¦ we must face the possibility that repeated atomic explosions would lead to a degree of general radioactivity which no one could tolerate or escape."</q></blockquote> Surely, the Prime Minister should consult with his scientific advisers to get some accurate information on this matter, because, I understand, it is possible to obtain it.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-d8a99d3a-10bf-4a09-9fc5-55b9c4e216c9" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1954-11-09/debates/7c94ea06-d5eb-425c-864e-c148817f910d/NuclearAndAtomicExplosions#contribution-d8a99d3a-10bf-4a09-9fc5-55b9c4e216c9">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-80a66ceb-7f25-4c00-93bd-1bf7d6594c6b">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-80a66ceb-7f25-4c00-93bd-1bf7d6594c6b">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-80a66ceb-7f25-4c00-93bd-1bf7d6594c6b">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-80a66ceb-7f25-4c00-93bd-1bf7d6594c6b">
                The Prime Minister
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-80a66ceb-7f25-4c00-93bd-1bf7d6594c6b" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1954-11-09/debates/7c94ea06-d5eb-425c-864e-c148817f910d/NuclearAndAtomicExplosions#contribution-80a66ceb-7f25-4c00-93bd-1bf7d6594c6b">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">I have not had an opportunity of verifying the quotation to which the hon. Member refers.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-80a66ceb-7f25-4c00-93bd-1bf7d6594c6b" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
